videos.headline: Arkansas State coach attended to on sidelines
videos.description: Arkansas State assistant athletic director Scotty Conley appears to collapse on the sideline and is immediately attended to by medical personnel.

videos.headline: App St. WR goes high for the TD grab
videos.description: Appalachian State wide receiver Corey Sutton makes the great TD catch over the defender.

videos.headline: App St. RB walks into the end zone for TD
videos.description: Appalachian State capitalizes on the turnover and gets the 1-yard touchdown run by Darrynton Evans.

videos.headline: App St. RB hurts ankle after TD run
videos.description: Appalachian State running back Jalin Moore has to be carted off the field after scoring the 27-yard touchdown.
